    "contentHtml": "\n    <div class=\"template-doc\" style=\"\">\n      <div style=\"color: rgb(22, 35, 59); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 22px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-size: 42px;\">2027도 한국대학교 수험표</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; font-weight: 700;\"><br></p>\n      </div>\n\n<table style=\"color: rgb(22, 35, 59); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; width: 700px; border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed; font-size: 15px; max-width: none;\">\n        <colgroup><col style=\"width: 192px;\"><col style=\"width: 85px;\"><col style=\"width: 163px;\"><col style=\"width: 86px;\"><col style=\"width: 174px;\"></colgroup>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <th class=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rowspan=\"6\" colspan=\"1\">#수험생사진<br></th><th style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">수험번호</th>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">#수험번호<br></td>\n            <th style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">모집시기</th>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">#모집시기<br></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">성&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;명</th>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">#이름<br></td>\n            <th style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">전 형 명</th>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">#전형<br></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">생년월일</th>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">#생년월일<br></td>\n            <th style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">모집단위</th>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">#모집단위<br></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">고사건물</th>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">#고사건물<br></td>\n            <th style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">전 공 명</th>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">#전공<br></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">고 사 실</th>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">#고사실<br></td>\n            <th style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">시험날짜</th>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">#시험날짜<br></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">조</th>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">#조<br></td>\n            <th style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">시&nbsp; &nbsp; 간</th>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 12px 14px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">#시간<br></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n\n      <table style=\"color: rgb(22, 35, 59); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 18px;\">\n        <colgroup><col style=\"width: 24px;\"><col style=\"width: 24px;\"><col style=\"width: 24px;\"></colgroup><tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <th colspan=\"3\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 10px 12px; text-align: center; font-weight: 700; background: rgb(246, 248, 252); vertical-align: top;\">\n              시험 시간 안내\n            </th>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 10px 8px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">\n              <strong>1교시</strong><br>\n              08:40 - 10:00\n            </td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 10px 8px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">\n              <strong>2교시</strong><br>\n              10:30 - 12:10\n            </td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 10px 8px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">\n              <strong>점심시간</strong><br>\n              12:10 - 13:00\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 10px 8px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\">\n              <strong>3교시</strong><br>\n              13:10 - 14:20\n            </td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 10px 8px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">\n              <strong>4교시</strong><br>\n              14:50 - 16:30\n            </td>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 10px 8px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">\n              <strong>5교시</strong><br>\n              17:00 - 17:45\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 18px; line-height: 1.7;\">\n        <p style=\"color: rgb(22, 35, 59); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700;\">[유의사항]</p>\n        <p style=\"color: rgb(22, 35, 59); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px;\">1. 반드시 신분증과 수험표를 함께 지참해야 합니다.</p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(22, 35, 59);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 35, 59); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: initial;\">※</span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 35, 59); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: initial; font-size: 14px;\">주민등록증, 청소년증, 운전면허증, 여권, 사진과 생년월일이 기재된 학생증, 행정복지센터 발급 임시신분증</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(22, 35, 59);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;※ 학생증에 생년월일 또는 사진이 없는 경우 학생증과 학교생활기록부를 함께 지참 시 신분증으로 인정</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(22, 35, 59);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;※ 모바일신분증(모바일 주민등록증, 모바일 운전면허증 등) 및 신분증 사본은 신분증으로 인정되지 않음</span></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(22, 35, 59); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px;\">2. 시험 시작 30분 전까지 지정된 고사실에 입실해야 합니다.</p>\n        <p style=\"color: rgb(22, 35, 59); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3. 휴대전화 및 전자기기 소지는 제한됩니다.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(22, 35, 59); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px;\"><br></p></div><br><img class=\"template-generated-object template-generated-object-qrcode\" data-template-object-type=\"qrcode\" data-template-object-source=\"examineeNo\" src=\"http://localhost:3000/api/template-objects/qrcode.svg?value=123100001\" alt=\"123100001 QR코드\" title=\"수험번호 QR코드\" style=\"width: 81px; height: 81px; position: absolute; left: 177px; top: 881px; margin: 0px; z-index: 2;\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"uni-0000.png\" class=\"\" style=\"height: 63px; width: 200px; position: absolute; left: 362px; top: 887px; margin: 0px; z-index: 2;\"></div>\n  "
